                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5943" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0432</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8318 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">立马长安终有日，百战更始得人心——中移在线陕西分公司人力资源管理的破局之战</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Eventually one day dominate chang&#39;an will be realize , the source of winning all is the popular sentiment——Breaking battle of human resources management of China Mobile Online Shaanxi Branch</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘立，楼旭明，贾卫峰，赵占平，邹熙，许元，刘燕云，曹润康，马潇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国移动在线服务有限公司陕西分公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源改革；人才招聘；薪酬优化；人文关怀</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Human Resources Reform; Talent Recruitment; Salary Optimization; Humanistic Care </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了中国移动在线服务有限公司陕西分公司（以下简称“中移在线陕西分公司”）的人力资源改革历程。中移在线陕西分公司分离之初在人力资源方面存在许多问题，例如员工受教育水平低，专业型人才紧缺，员工缺乏积极性和幸福感等。中移在线陕西分公司为完成业务转型升级，不断寻求解决方案，打破固有思维，学习成功经验，在人才招聘、人才培训、薪酬优化、人文关怀、绩效考核五个方面进行了人力资源改革。在新的人力资源管理体系帮助下，中移在线陕西分公司成功摆脱困境，在一年内从全国倒数第二名跃至前三名内，成功地完成了业务转型。通过对本案例的分析和讨论，学员可以进一步理解人力资源管理在企业经营过程中的重要性，同时此案例也可为企业优化人力资源管理体系提供参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the human resource reform process of China Mobile Online Services Limited Shaanxi Branch ( hereinafter referred to as &quot; China Mobile Online Shaanxi Branch &quot;) . Among the many problems of the separation of the China Mobile Online Shaanxi Branch , such as low education level of employees, shortage of professional talents, and lack of enthusiasm and happiness of employees. In order to complete the business transformation and upgrading, China Mobile Online Shaanxi Branch has constantly sought solutions, broken its inherent thinking and learned successful experience, and has carried out human resource reform in five aspects: talent recruitment, talent training, salary optimization, humanistic care and performance assessment. With the help of the new human resources management system, the China Mobile Online Shaanxi Branch successfully got rid of difficulties and jumped from the last place to the top three within one year, and completed the successful transformation of business. Through the analysis and discussion of this case, the students can further understand the importance of human resource management in the operation process of the enterprise, and this case can also provide a reference for the enterprise to optimize the human resource management system.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术工具和社交媒体营销策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-01</td>
